位則報212.9點，指數按月持平。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32017594&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=117012292168aec2dae86610_82133352"/><published>2025-08-27T13:00:25+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>26cf853a8195aaa16783b02d1a7bba73</id><title>吹緊施政報告有利好措施</title><updated>2025-08-27T13:08:51+08:00</updated><author><name>阿柒回歸</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-27T13:08:51+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573751942"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573751942"&gt;本港樓價連升四個月上月私人住宅售價指數按月升0.4%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ftc%2Ffinance%2F68ae68585038aced1aacced3%3Futm_source%3Dnewsappshare%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=94de4088e101059c484c9e21bacf10b8&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://news.tvb.com/tc/finance/ ... utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32017599&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=117012292168aec2dae86610_82133352"/><published>2025-08-27T13:08:51+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>fddbf3ed6dd08b6cffd45ff4d5b8d984</id><title>Hibor 不了？ 滙豐推新定息按揭計劃 減息0.45厘至2.73厘 分析籲毋須急決定</title><updated>2025-08-27T13:42:28+08:00</updated><author><name>aq6aq6</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-27T13:42:28+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573752300"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573752300"&gt;滙豐推新定息按揭計劃減息0.4